The use of the MS COCO dataset and VGG_CNN_M_1024 model also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions improvements to the demo program, which could fall under natural language processing (cs.CL) or multimedia (cs.MM).
